snippet.title: Just Get Through Official Trailer 2015
snippet.description:
Official Just Get Through Game Trailer with Gameplay - 2015
Get 'Just Get Through' on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/338190

Just Get Through is a fast, randomly generated platformer game with roguelike elements. Featuring a destructible environment, a sandbox mode, user-created custom levels, color palletes, deadly traps, explosions and much more. This game is the first of its kind.

And this is Just Get Through's official Trailer.


Music by JGaudio


Get the game: http://store.steampowered.com/app/338190

"Just Get Through Trailer"

Just Get Through was developed by Jonathan Mannshoven in GameMaker: Studio
